26:34.034 --> 26:35.705
‐ Elaine. Hey, Elaine.

26:35.705 --> 26:37.082
Hey, turn this bullshit off,
will you?

26:37.082 --> 26:38.251
We got the Mets playing.

26:38.251 --> 26:39.879
‐ You're in Manhattan, Gordo.

26:39.879 --> 26:41.675
We watch the Yankees
in Manhattan.

26:41.675 --> 26:43.344
‐ You tell him, Elaine.

26:43.344 --> 26:45.181
‐ Get yourself to Flushing,
you want the Mets.

26:45.181 --> 26:47.144
‐ Yeah, I might just go to
Flushing, cheaper beers there,

26:47.144 --> 26:48.772
