you're in Flushing.

26:51.611 --> 26:54.283
[gentle rock music playing]

26:54.283 --> 26:57.122
[indistinct conversation]

26:57.122 --> 26:59.544
‐ I thought you said
his girlfriend's name was Liz?

26:59.544 --> 27:02.967
‐ The one I met was named Liz.

27:02.967 --> 27:05.639
‐ Are they still together?
‐ [muttering] No...

27:05.639 --> 27:08.979
‐ What does that mean?
‐ It means I work with the guy.

27:08.979 --> 27:11.192
I don't question
his personal life.

27:13.029 --> 27:14.949
‐ You spend most of your time
with him.

27:14.949 --> 27:16.745
You travel with him.
‐ Yeah, Heather.

27:16.745 --> 27:19.249
I love these guys.
I'd trust them with my life.

27:19.249 --> 27:21.420
But we don't‐‐we're
not the same.

27:21.420 --> 27:24.301
We don't all want
the same things.

27:24.301 --> 27:25.638
‐ So tell me.

27:25.638 --> 27:29.102
‐ Tell you what?
‐ Tell me what you want.

27:29.102 --> 27:31.357
‐ [softly] This.

27:31.357 --> 27:33.361
‐ A blonde girl?
‐ That blonde girl.

27:33.361 --> 27:35.448
‐ Not too many of those
in Beirut?

27:35.448 --> 27:37.912
‐ Not too many Arabs
in small town Ohio.

27:37.912 --> 27:40.208
‐ So we're both exotics?

27:40.208 --> 27:41.878
‐ I'm attracted
to the difference.

27:41.878 --> 27:44.091
I can admit it.

27:44.091 --> 27:46.638
‐ Okay.
[chuckles softly]

27:46.638 --> 27:49.351
‐ But that's not what really
draws me in.

27:49.351 --> 27:51.606
‐ What draws you in?

27:51.606 --> 27:54.152
‐ Where we connect.

27:54.152 --> 27:56.240
‐ Where's that?
‐ [chuckles]

27:57.200 --> 27:59.204
Here...

27:59.204 --> 28:02.002
and here...

28:02.002 --> 28:03.880
and there.

28:03.880 --> 28:05.968
‐ [whack]
‐ [laughs]

28:05.968 --> 28:07.345
‐ Nah, I'm telling you,
I miss it.

28:07.345 --> 28:08.724
‐ Really?
‐ All the time.

28:08.724 --> 28:10.143
‐ Upstate New York?
‐ Yeah.

28:10.143 --> 28:12.105
‐ What the hell is there
to do up there?

28:12.105 --> 28:14.527
‐ What is there to do?
Well, I‐‐I used to fish.

28:14.527 --> 28:16.155
I mean, there's
a beautiful stream

28:16.155 --> 28:17.825
