29:19.114 --> 29:21.410
Hey.

29:21.410 --> 29:23.999
‐ What are you talking about?

29:23.999 --> 29:27.882
‐ Come on, who are you to them?

29:27.882 --> 29:30.136
You're me.

29:30.136 --> 29:31.723
You're my eyes and my ears.

29:31.723 --> 29:35.396
That's why they don't want you
