to force me out.

30:12.888 --> 30:16.311
‐ Why?
‐ I don't know.

30:16.311 --> 30:18.775
‐ What's going on?
‐ I don't fucking know.

30:20.779 --> 30:23.117
You get your ass on
that train tomorrow morning,

30:23.117 --> 30:25.329
